{"data": [{"id": "4745475", "title": "Dave: An Old-School Payday Lender In Disguise", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2165047379/image_2165047379.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt='gold coins and a neon billboard displaying the words \"PAYDAY LOANS\"' data-id=\"2165047379\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"864px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2165047379/image_2165047379.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2165047379/image_2165047379.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2165047379/image_2165047379.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2165047379/image_2165047379.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2165047379/image_2165047379.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2165047379/image_2165047379.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2165047379/image_2165047379.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2165047379/image_2165047379.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Love Employee/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>As credit <a href=\"https://fred.stlouisfed.org/series/REVOLSL\" rel=\"nofollow\">card debt levels soar</a>, many seek new ways to borrow money. In recent years, we've seen the rise of numerous fintech companies focused on changing personal lending. As I <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4728494-affirm-stock-buy-now-pay-later-may-be-superior-credit-card-lending\">previously discussed</a></p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2165047379/image_2165047379.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745475-dave-stock-old-school-payday-lender-in-disguise-reasonably-valued", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 06:09:29"}, {"id": "4745474", "title": "Tracking John Paulson's Paulson & Company Portfolio - Q3 2024 Update", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/531467608/image_531467608.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"CDS cubics acronym\" data-id=\"531467608\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"864px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/531467608/image_531467608.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/531467608/image_531467608.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/531467608/image_531467608.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/531467608/image_531467608.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/531467608/image_531467608.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/531467608/image_531467608.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/531467608/image_531467608.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/531467608/image_531467608.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">TimArbaev</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>This article is part of a series that provides an ongoing analysis of the changes made to John Paulson\u2019s 13F stock portfolio on a quarterly basis. It is based on Paulson\u2019s regulatory <a href=\"https://www.sec.gov/Archives/edgar/data/1035674/000101359424000980/0001013594-24-000980-index.htm\" rel=\"nofollow\">13F Form</a> filed on 11/14/2024. Please visit</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/531467608/image_531467608.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745474-tracking-john-paulsons-paulson-and-company-portfolio-q3-2024-update", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 05:21:20"}, {"id": "4745471", "title": "IBHF: A Fixed-Maturity ETF I Love", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2182119357/image_2182119357.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt='Stack of coins, a wooden block labeled \"2025,\" a magnifying glass, and a 2025 calendar. Financial goals and planning for the upcoming year, emphasizing careful budgeting and investment strategies' data-id=\"2182119357\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"960px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2182119357/image_2182119357.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2182119357/image_2182119357.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2182119357/image_2182119357.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2182119357/image_2182119357.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2182119357/image_2182119357.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2182119357/image_2182119357.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2182119357/image_2182119357.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2182119357/image_2182119357.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">PhanuwatNandee/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>In principle, bonds are the simplest of all investment instruments, as they simply promise to pay you fixed amounts of money on fixed future dates. For many goals when I know I'll need a specific amount of money</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2182119357/image_2182119357.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745471-ibhf-fixed-maturity-etf-love", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 05:07:16"}, {"id": "4745465", "title": "Hapag-Lloyd: A Look Beneath The Surface", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1817176691/image_1817176691.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Crane operator picking up a Hapag-Lloyd sea container\" data-id=\"1817176691\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1817176691/image_1817176691.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1817176691/image_1817176691.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1817176691/image_1817176691.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1817176691/image_1817176691.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1817176691/image_1817176691.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1817176691/image_1817176691.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1817176691/image_1817176691.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1817176691/image_1817176691.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">VanderWolf-Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Hapag-Lloyd Aktiengesellschaft (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/HLAGF\" title=\"Hapag-Lloyd Aktiengesellschaft\">OTCPK:HLAGF</a>), a top-five container shipping company primarily focused on European routes (Transatlantic and Europe-Asia), recently released an <a href=\"https://www.hapag-lloyd.com/content/dam/website/downloads/ir/HLAG_9M_2024_EN.pdf\" rel=\"nofollow\">upbeat interim report for Q3 2024</a> and raised full-year guidance on the back of this strength. This came</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1817176691/image_1817176691.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745465-hapag-lloyd-stock-look-beneath-the-surface-reiterate-hold", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 04:45:54"}, {"id": "4745462", "title": "British American Tobacco: The Ideal Company To Face An Uncertain 2025", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/626868346/image_626868346.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Girl smoking\" data-id=\"626868346\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/626868346/image_626868346.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/626868346/image_626868346.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/626868346/image_626868346.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/626868346/image_626868346.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/626868346/image_626868346.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/626868346/image_626868346.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/626868346/image_626868346.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/626868346/image_626868346.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">markophotoart/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>The Fed's decision to cut rates only twice in 2025 has sown doubts among investors. High rates for longer means limiting economic growth and not giving a boost to demand for credit. The decision was made on</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/626868346/image_626868346.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745462-british-american-tobacco-ideal-company-to-face-uncertain-2025", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 04:19:06"}, {"id": "4745458", "title": "Descartes: The Quiet Canadian Compounder - Why Descartes Remains My Top Software Pick", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1329183101/image_1329183101.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Global Communication Network (World Map Credits To Nasa)\" data-id=\"1329183101\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"864px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1329183101/image_1329183101.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1329183101/image_1329183101.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1329183101/image_1329183101.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1329183101/image_1329183101.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1329183101/image_1329183101.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1329183101/image_1329183101.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1329183101/image_1329183101.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1329183101/image_1329183101.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">imaginima</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2><strong>Introduction </strong></h2> <p>Descartes Systems (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/DSGX\" title=\"The Descartes Systems Group Inc.\">DSGX</a></span>) was the first company I covered here on Seeking Alpha. Interestingly, it was also the first stock I pitched to my Boss a few years ago during my time as a Fund Manager Assistant at</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1329183101/image_1329183101.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745458-descartes-quiet-canadian-compounder-my-top-software-pick-strong-buy", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 04:06:36"}, {"id": "4745469", "title": "Q3 GDP Third Estimate: Real GDP At 3.1%, Above Forecast", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1496930327/image_1496930327.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Gross domestic product or GDP. Business, economy, trade, Consumption, and Investment. An arrow sign pointing downwards and up in a wooden block\" data-id=\"1496930327\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"864px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1496930327/image_1496930327.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1496930327/image_1496930327.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1496930327/image_1496930327.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1496930327/image_1496930327.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1496930327/image_1496930327.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1496930327/image_1496930327.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1496930327/image_1496930327.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1496930327/image_1496930327.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Khanchit Khirisutchalual</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>By Jennifer Nash</em></p> <p>The U.S. economy grew above expectations during the third quarter of this year. Real gross domestic product increased at an annual rate of 3.1% in Q3 2024, according to the third estimate. The latest estimate is above the forecasted</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1496930327/image_1496930327.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745469-q3-gdp-third-estimate-real-gdp-at-3-1-percent-above-forecast", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 04:00:00"}, {"id": "4745463", "title": "U.S. Fed Cuts Rates By 25 Bps, Signals Fewer Cuts In 2025", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1692418614/image_1692418614.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Percentage sign\" data-id=\"1692418614\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1692418614/image_1692418614.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1692418614/image_1692418614.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1692418614/image_1692418614.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1692418614/image_1692418614.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1692418614/image_1692418614.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1692418614/image_1692418614.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1692418614/image_1692418614.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1692418614/image_1692418614.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Richard Drury</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>The U.S. Federal Reserve has lowered its overnight rate by another 25 basis points to 4.5%. Hafiz Noordin, Vice President &amp; Director, Active Fixed Income Portfolio Management at TD Asset Management, speaks with MoneyTalk\u2019s Anthony Okolie about the decision and why policymakers are suggesting</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1692418614/image_1692418614.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745463-us-fed-cuts-rates-by-25-bps-signals-fewer-cuts-in-2025", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 03:45:00"}, {"id": "4745464", "title": "Scholastic Corporation 2025 Q2 - Results - Earnings Call Presentation", "description": "<p>The following slide deck was published by Scholastic Corporation in conjunction with their 2025 Q2 earnings call.</p> <p><figure class=\"sa-presentation paywall-full-content invisible\" data-id=\"106255\"></figure></p>", "image": null, "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745464-scholastic-corporation-2025-q2-results-earnings-call-presentation", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 03:38:21"}, {"id": "4745454", "title": "Nvidia's Sellers May Be Missing The Big Picture", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/502379459/image_502379459.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Nvidia World Headquarters\" data-id=\"502379459\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"5616px\" height=\"3744px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/502379459/image_502379459.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/502379459/image_502379459.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/502379459/image_502379459.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/502379459/image_502379459.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/502379459/image_502379459.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/502379459/image_502379459.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/502379459/image_502379459.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/502379459/image_502379459.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">JasonDoiy</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>I built a strong position in NVIDIA (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/NVDA\" title=\"NVIDIA Corporation\">NVDA</a></span>) when the most prominent generative AI tool so far (ChatGPT) was first introduced to the mass public (at the end of 2022). Since then, I've been very bullish on NVIDIA and have regularly added</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/502379459/image_502379459.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745454-nvidias-sellers-fail-to-see-the-big-picture", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 03:32:10"}]}